<i>noun</i>: 고문관 [고문관] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>고문관 [고문관]</dt><br>
<dd>1. councilor; adviser; counselor</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 분야에 대해 의견을 말하거나 도움을 주는 직책.</dd><br>
<dd>A title whose holder gives opinions or helps people in a certain field.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slow-witted person</dd><br>
<dd>군대나 회사 등에서 말을 잘 알아듣지 못하고 실수가 잦은 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person in an army or company, who does not catch what others mean easily and who makes a lot of mistakes.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>